---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="pepprime | Company" description="About pepprime peptide supplier.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-14 sm:px-6 sm:py-16">
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.04fr_0.96fr]">
      <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-blue-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft sm:p-8">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-brand-blue">Company</div>
        <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">pepprime</h1>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm leading-8 text-slate-600 sm:text-base">
          <p>
            pepprime is presented as a peptide-focused supplier serving customers who want clear product information, visible pricing, and direct communication.
          </p>
          <p>
            The company website is designed around professional product display, fast worldwide shipping communication, and a strong laboratory-inspired visual identity.
          </p>
          <p>
            The current catalog includes multiple peptide products across different strengths, with direct inquiry available by WhatsApp or email.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-6">
        <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-blue-100 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-navy to-brand-blue p-8 text-white shadow-soft">
          <div class="label-pill label-pill--light">pepprime Standard</div>
          <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Blue biotech presentation</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-8 text-blue-50 sm:text-base">
            A cleaner company profile helps customers focus on product range, pricing, support, and direct contact instead of unnecessary filler sections.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-blue-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-glow">
            <div class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-950">Fast response</div>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">Quick communication by email and WhatsApp for product and shipping inquiry.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-blue-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-glow">
            <div class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-950">Product focus</div>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">Clear product photos, visible prices, and direct inquiry across the peptide catalog.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
